The EAC Secretariat is organizing a multi-sectoral Ministerial meeting to take place on Monday, Jan. 10, 2022, that will consider the adoption of EACPass, a harmonized system to facilitate cross-border movement. The EAC Secretariat is organizing a multi-sectoral Ministerial meeting to take place on Monday, Jan. 10, 2022, that will consider the adoption of EACPass, a harmonized system to facilitate cross-border movement.